Points of Attack for Hackathon

We are creating a Wikipedia spell checker as a Chrome extension

1. Learn how to make a chrome extension
2. Create GitHub repository
3. Find an english language database
4. Code a way to access that database
5. Code a spellchecker for all lowercase words. Ignore capital proper nouns, words in quotation marks, hyperlinked words.
6. Code a wikipedia article processorâ€”process the text check it.
7. Code a way to display red bars under wrong words
